c9e49a3177f6135b2cedc00b0bc36ef7421a34941349bcfe242702dcfb5ebf13907d0ae8f8af1e26065b21e53f29e69c1fe36fd6724bfbb86556c3df828c8f23  osmo-0.2.10-build-mo.patch"
